snippet.title: What Does It Mean to Play Game~B? w/ Jordan Hall -- A Sensemaking Wormhole
snippet.description:
This "Sensemaking Wormhole" was facilitated by Jordan Hall (https://www.youtube.com/user/jordangreenhall) and was organized and hosted by Peter Limberg of the Intellectual Explorers Club (https://www.intellectualexplorers.club) in the Game B Coffee House.

About the Game~B Coffee House (gameb.coffee)
The Game~B Coffeehouse (https://gameb.coffee) is an open virtual community space for workshops like this or spur-of-the-moment conversations with others that are interested in Game B. It is a Zoom room that's open and available for anyone to join 24/7 via https://gameb.coffee . 

To learn more about Game B, consider looking at "On Game~B" from James Allen (https://twitter.com/SeamusOhAilin): https://docs.google.com/document/d/1VqIGuIafjW9WSVeBJf7jWFfuOXBiUZLWk2pqJOhNESc
